程序包 org.cloudbus.cloudsim.container.resourceAllocators

类 ContainerAllocationPolicy

java.lang.Object
org.cloudbus.cloudsim.container.resourceAllocators.ContainerAllocationPolicy
直接已知子类:
ContainerAllocationPolicySimple, PowerContainerAllocationPolicy
public abstract class ContainerAllocationPolicy
extends java.lang.Object
ContainerAllocationPolicy is an abstract class that represents the provisioning policy of vms to ContainerContainerGoogle in a Datacentre.
从以下版本开始:
CloudSim Toolkit 3.0
